To compile this projet, the following requiremens are needed:
  * C++11 compiler
  * Cmake
  
To boot strap it, type in the top directory:
	$ cmake .

To select debugging mode, edit CMakeCache.txt and fix the following line:
	//Choose the type of build, options are: None Debug Release RelWithDebInfo
	// MinSizeRel ...
	CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE:STRING=Debug

To compile the project in the top directory:
	$ make .

Test are contained in the directory "test".

A ready to develop application skeleton can be found in main.cpp.
